'''Sándor Ádám''' (February 1, 1892 in [[Budapest]] – ?) was a [[Hungary|Hungarian]] [[water polo]] player who competed in the [[1912 Summer Olympics]].

He was part of the Hungarian team in the [[Water polo at the 1912 Summer Olympics|1912 tournament]].

